01:53.146 --> 01:54.948 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I think it's an absolute
disgrace.

01:54.982 --> 02:00.454 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The bombshell
burst Tuesday
evening, when CNN reported the
president-elect

02:00.487 --> 02:04.491 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
