the claims.

02:36.857 --> 02:41.328 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Today, Mr. Trump insisted he
wouldn't put
himself in such a position.

02:41.361 --> 02:47.501 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: I told many
people, be careful,
because you don't want to see
yourself on

02:47.534 --> 02:49.169 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
television.

02:49.202 --> 02:52.506 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There are cameras all over the
place, and,
again, not just Russia, all
over.

02:52.539 --> 02:54.975 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Does anyone really believe that
story?

02:55.008 --> 02:59.046 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
