the consequences.

03:11.191 --> 03:16.596 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And he accused
CNN of being
fake news, and brushed off
persistent attempts

03:16.630 --> 03:19.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
