turned out to
be so false and fake out.

03:41.521 --> 03:44.091 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think it's a disgrace, and I
say that.

03:44.124 --> 03:47.594 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that's something that Nazi
Germany would
have done, and did do.

03:47.627 --> 03:52.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: On Russian
hacking more broadly,
the president-elect suggested an
upside to

03:52.799 --> 03:55.902 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
