computers
and e-mails.

03:55.936 --> 04:00.540 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: The hacking is bad
and it shouldn't
be done.

04:00.574 --> 04:02.342 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But look at the things that were
hacked.

04:02.375 --> 04:07.147 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Look at what was learned from
that hacking,
that Hillary Clinton got the
questions to

04:07.180 --> 04:10.183 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the debate and didn't report it?

04:10.217 --> 04:12.018 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's a horrible thing.

04:12.052 --> 04:15.622 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Likewise, he
acknowledged the
intelligence verdict that
President Vladimir

04:15.655 --> 04:18.825 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
