he didn't leave
it there.

04:18.859 --> 04:24.397 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: I think it was
Russia, but I
think we also get hacked by
other countries

04:24.431 --> 04:26.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
