04:26.199 --> 04:30.504 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And looking
ahead, Mr. Trump
suggested the hacking will not
necessarily

04:30.537 --> 04:32.606 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
