Putin.

04:32.639 --> 04:37.043 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: If Putin likes
Donald Trump,
guess what, folks?

04:37.077 --> 04:39.112 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's called an asset, not a
liability.

04:39.146 --> 04:46.052 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
