04:48.188 --> 04:49.422 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
You will see that.

04:49.456 --> 04:52.359 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Russia will respect our country
more.

04:52.392 --> 04:54.127 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He shouldn't have done it.

04:54.161 --> 04:55.996 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I don't believe he will be doing
it more.

04:56.029 --> 05:00.867 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: There were also
questions about
the Trump Organization's
business ties to

05:00.901 --> 05:02.969 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
