any.

05:03.003 --> 05:05.972 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: We could make
deals in Russia
very easily if we wanted to.

05:06.006 --> 05:08.675 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
