think that
would be a conflict.

05:08.708 --> 05:13.413 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So I have no loans, no dealings
and no current
pending deals.

05:13.446 --> 05:18.618 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Mr. Trump has not
released
tax returns to verify his
claims, and he said

05:18.652 --> 05:23.423 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
