federal audit
is finished.

05:23.456 --> 05:29.529 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He also declined to say whether
his associates
or campaign staff had contact
with Russian

05:29.563 --> 05:32.132 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
officials during the campaign.

05:32.165 --> 05:39.206 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
