attempted to
talk to people in various
communities to see

08:36.516 --> 08:41.287 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
whether or not the allegations
seemed credible
to them.

08:41.321 --> 08:46.593 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think the point that we're at
now, it's
really not about our
organization or anyone

08:46.626 --> 08:48.762 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
else verifying the specific
facts.

08:48.795 --> 08:51.998 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
The FBI is conducting an
investigation.

08:52.031 --> 08:55.301 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We will expect -- there are very
specific
allegations in this document.

08:55.335 --> 08:58.738 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Those allegations can either be
proven true
or proven false.

08:58.772 --> 09:03.810 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so we should expect some
answers that
provide some additional clarity.

09:03.843 --> 09:07.614 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One important note is just
because a single
fact in the document is true, it
